reviewText: When I saw this DVD on "amazon.com" and saw the cast, I just had to buy it. Isabella Camille is a beautiful and sexy girl I saw on other DVDs, so I wanted to see more of her. Her scene doesn't disappoint me. It's very, very sexy. A stunning girl in very sexy poses is a winner for sure! Krystal Klein has a nice scene too. I notice these two girls much more than Crissy Moran or Erika Jordan who also appear in the DVD. Each person has his own opinion, and some men may like Crissy and Erica, but Isabella Camille is peerless to me. 5 stars aren't enough for her.
